The paper deals with the problem of identifying causal relations among variables, which is a fundamental problem in artificial intelligence and machine learning. Therefore, cs.AI and cs.LG are the most likely sub-categories. The paper also involves information theory and graph theory, which suggests cs.IT and cs.DS as likely sub-categories. Finally, the paper deals with the problem of designing experiments, which could fall under cs.SI.
